rom%20a%20large%2C%20phase-3%20clinical%20trial%2C%20testing%20Zepbound%20(the%20drug%20name%20for%20tirzepatide)%20as%20a%20treatment%20for%20sleep%20apnea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20yearlong%20trial%20of%20469%20people%2C%20patients%20with%20moderate%20to%20severe%20sleep%20apnea%20experienced%2C%20on%20average%2C%20roughly%2027-30%20fewer%20apnea%20events%20per%20hour%20of%20sleep%20when%20they%20took%20weekly%20injections%20of%20Zepbound%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20Zepbound%20users%20also%20lost%2C%20on%20average%2C%20nearly%20a%20fifth%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20(18%25)%20while%20on%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%2C%20which%20analysts%20say%20may%20be%20on%20pace%20to%20become%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-16%2Feli-lilly-closer-to-joining-magnificent-seven-in-1-trillion-market-cap-club%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrillion-dollar%20drug%20company%20soon%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expecting%20to%20submit%20these%20results%20to%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20by%20mid-year.%20The%20company%20will%20disclose%20the%20full%20data%20at%20the%20American%20Diabetes%20Association%20conference%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20FDA%20green-lights%20this%20use%2C%20tirzepatide%20could%20be%20approved%20for%20moderate%20to%20severe%20sleep%20apnea%20patients%20with%20obesity%20in%20a%20year%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOzempic%20and%20Mounjaro%3A%20not%20just%20for%20diabetes%20and%20weight%20loss%20anymore%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGLP-1%20drugs%20first%20emerged%20roughly%2015%20years%20ago%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%20and%20help%20control%20blood%20sugar.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20as%20the%20drugs%20have%20gotten%20more%20powerful%20and%20easier%20to%20use%2C%20doctors%20and%20patients%20have%20started%20to%20discover%20that%20they%20can%20also%20help%20promote%20significant%20weight%20loss%20by%20helping%20people%20feel%20fuller%20and%20more%20satisfied%20with%20less%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20GLP-1%20drugs%20have%20been%20indicated%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EObesity%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fpress-announcements%2Ffda-approves-first-treatment-reduce-risk-serious-heart-problems-specifically-adults-obesity-or%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20clinical%20trials%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-treat-addiction-alzheimers-depression-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20drugs%20have%20also%20shown%20some%20promise%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20treating%20other%20conditions%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ENon-alcoholic%20fatty%20liver%20disease%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAddiction%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EDepression%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EParkinson's%20and%20Alzheimer's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ECancer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EThese%20breakthroughs%20may%20be%20tied%20to%20the%20gut-brain%20connection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20of%20neurons%2C%20their%20cell%20body%20(soma)%20is%20pink%20and%20yellow%2C%20the%20dendrites%20and%20axons%20are%20the%20color%20purple.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652db34d6561dd877e7bf576%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScientists%20think%20that%20the%20main%20reason%20GLP-1%20drugs%20work%20well%20is%20because%20of%20their%20effect%20on%20our%20body's%20gut-brain%20connection.%3Cp%3EKATERYNA%20KON%2FSCIENCE%20PHOTO%20LIBRARY%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20point%20to%20the%20way%20that%20weight%20loss%20can%20help%20out%20with%20many%20of%20the%20above%20conditions%2C%20saying%20the%20impacts%20of%20GLP-1%20dru