ool%2C%20the%20student%20debt%20that%20often%20follows%20them%20post-graduation%20can%20significantly%20impact%20their%20ability%20to%20progress%20financially.%20For%20example%2C%20per%20the%20survey%2C%2071%25%20of%20currently%20and%20previously%20enrolled%20student-loan%20borrowers%20reported%20%26quot%3Bdelaying%20at%20least%20one%20significant%20life%20event%20because%20of%20their%20student%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%2029%25%20of%20them%20delayed%20buying%20a%20home%2C%2028%25%20of%20them%20delayed%20buying%20a%20car%2C%2015%25%20of%20them%20delayed%20having%20children%2C%20and%2013%25%20of%20them%20delayed%20getting%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20delaying%20life%20events%20didn't%20discriminate%20by%20student-loan%20balance%2C%20as%20the%20report%20found%3A%2098%25%20of%20overall%20respondents%20with%20balances%20of%20%2475%2C000%20or%20more%20reported%20pushing%20off%20those%20events%2C%20with%2063%25%20of%20respondents%20with%20balances%20less%20than%20%2410%2C000%20reporting%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEspecially%20given%20how%20many%20people%20have%20loans%20and%20how%20much%20%5Bin%5D%20loans%20they%20have%2C%20it's%20really%20scary%20to%20me%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20it%20will%20be%20hanging%20over%20a%20lot%20of%20people's%20heads%20for%20maybe%20their%20entire%20lives.%20I%20think%20it's%20cool%20that%20people%20are%20getting%20a%20college%20education%2C%20but%20I%20do%20worry%20about%20the%20financial%20repercussions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20currently%20enrolled%20student%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstories-of-student-loan-debt-hamster-wheel-borrowers-cant-escape-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20to%20a%20range%20of%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20have%20struggled%20to%20pay%20off%20their%20student%20loans%2C%20having%20to%20make%20sacrifices%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20