owed%2C%20Stonestreet%20was%20unable%20to%20work.%20Basista%20left%20her%20job%20as%20a%20regional%20sales%20manager%20to%20take%20a%20new%20sales%20role%20that%20allowed%20her%20more%20time%20at%20home%20while%20her%20partner%20recovered%2C%20but%20it%20came%20with%20a%20significant%20pay%20cut.%20As%20the%20couple's%20income%20plummeted%2C%20Stonestreet's%20insurance%20premiums%20soared%20to%20%241%2C200%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20we%20couldn't%20afford%20the%20mortgage%20and%20the%20car%20payments%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Stonestreet%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20conventional%20American%20lifestyle%20just%20wasn't%20in%20our%20reach%20anymore.%26quot%3B%20The%20couple%20sold%20their%20house%20in%20Denver%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20break%20even.%20Over%20the%20next%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20they%20hatched%20an%20escape%20plan.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20pair%20relocated%20to%20Cuenca%2C%20Ecuador%2C%20and%20continued%20working%20their%20old%20jobs%20remotely.%20Their%20monthly%20expenses%20dropped%20by%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasista%20and%20Stonestreet%20are%20part%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-from-us-to-france-without-visiting-first-worth-it-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemerging%20cohort%20of%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%2C%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-paris-finds-it-more-affordable-than-expected-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20living%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20seeking%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20elsewhere.%20They%20swap%20advice%20on%20Reddit%20boards%20like%20AmerExit%20(57%2C000%20members)%20and%20I%20Want%20Out%20(2%20million%20members)%2C%20consult%20with%20concierge%20relocation-service%20providers%20that%20cost%20a%20few%20hundred%20to%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20pop%2C%20and%20teach%20others%20how%20to%20follow%20in%20t