20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20temple's%20construction%20committee's%20chief%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENripendra%20Mishra%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Construction%20Committee%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20conceptualised%20the%20idea%20when%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20was%20on%20its%20final%20leg.%20The%20proposal%20was%20simple%3A%20to%20ensure%20that%20on%20every%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20the%20rays%20of%20the%20sun%20would%20hit%20the%20forehead%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20placed%20in%20the%20temple's%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20To%20make%20the%20PM's%20dream%20come%20true%2C%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20ensued%2C%20with%20experts%20and%20scientists%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20engaged%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ritual%20was%20carried%20out%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20photos%20of%20him%20watching%20a%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20event.%20The%20PM%20described%20the%20moment%20as%20%26quot%3Bwonderful%20and%20incomparable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Nalbari%20meeting%2C%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20witnessing%20the%20wonderful%20and%20incomparable%20moment%20of%20Surya%20Tilak%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya.%20This%20much-awaited%20moment%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20bliss%20for%20everyone.%20This%20Surya%20Tilak%20will%20illuminate%20every%20resolution%20of%20developed%20India%20with%20its%20divine%20energy%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20my%20Nalbari%20rally%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20on%20Ram%20Lalla.%20Like%20crores%20of%20Indians%2C%20this%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20moment%20for%20me.%20The%20grand%20Ram%20Navami%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20historic.%20May%20