%20spend%20could%20top%20that%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20talk%20about%20our%20specific%20numbers%2C%20but%20I%20think%20we're%20investing%20more%20than%20that%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20has%20already%20triggered%20a%20huge%20surge%20of%20investment%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0AI%20startups%20alone%20raised%20almost%20%2450%20billion%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.crunchbase.com%2Fai%2Fhot-startups-2023-openai-anthropic-forecast-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Crunchbase%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Hassabis'%20comments%20signal%20that%20competition%20to%20lead%20the%20AI%20sector%20is%20going%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20especially%20the%20case%20for%20companies%20like%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20are%20all%20engaged%20in%20an%20intense%20battle%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20first%20to%20claim%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20of%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AI%20with%20the%20capacity%20to%20match%20human%20reasoning%20and%20ingenuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChunky%20chips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20one%20company%20could%20spend%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20on%20a%20single%20technology%20that%20some%20think%20could%20be%20overhyped%20is%20eye-opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20considering%20where%20that%20spending%20could%20go.%20For%20starters%2C%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20development%20cost%20will%20be%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ai-chip-production-manufacturing-nvidia-labor-china-taiwan-korea-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echips%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20make%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20purchases%20for%20companies%20invested%20in%20the%20ra