jeffbnimble_opentowork-activity-7185340953677688832-bld1%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bogdan%20said%20that%20his%20entire%20career%20at%20Microsoft%20has%20been%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20ride%26quot%3B.%20But%20he%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20payoff%20for%20him%20came%20in%20the%20last%202%20years%20when%20he%20pitched%20and%20landed%20an%20L%26amp%3BD%20role%20in%20Windows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20premise%20was%20that%2C%20after%20successfully%20spreading%20a%20%26quot%3Blearn-it-all%26quot%3B%20mindset%20throughout%20the%20org%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20spread%20a%20%26quot%3Bteach-it-all%26quot%3B%20mindset%20to%20accompany%20this.%20I%20focused%20on%20organizing%20the%20learning%20investments%20for%20a%202%2C000-person%20org%2C%20and%20then%20worked%20to%20align%20that%20with%20learning%20%26amp%3B%20development%20offerings%20from%20our%20parent%20orgs%20and%20from%20central%20HR%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Mr%20Bogdan%20revealed%20that%20his%20job%20elimination%20was%20the%20result%20of%20HR%20adopting%20the%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model%20for%20L%26amp%3BD%20that%20he%20was%20pitching.%20%26quot%3BSadly%2C%20when%20my%20division%20already%20had%20their%20L%26amp%3BD%20team%20in%20place%2C%20there%20wasn't%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20abundant%20reflection%2C%20I%20have%20concluded%20that%20I%20am%20nowhere%20close%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BR%20word%26quot%3B.%20There%20is%20still%20so%20much%20that%20I%20want%20to%20contribute.%20So%20now%20begins%20the%20journey%20of%20finding%20my%20second%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-73-dies-after-medics-check-do-not-resuscitate-notice-of-wrong-patient-5459165%5C%22%3E%