di%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faaradhya-is-far-wiser-and-intelligent-than-i-was-at-her-age-says-navya-nanda-watch-exclusive-video%2Farticleshow%2F109367422.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi%20Kapoor's%20'Ulajh%E2%80%99%20teaser%20out%20now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713339532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109367408%2Cimgsize-17226.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fulajh-teaser-out-janhvi-kapoor-takes-on-high-stakes-world-of-ifs%2Farticleshow%2F109367436.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109367436.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJanhvi%20Kapoor's%20Ulajh%20teaser%20unravels%20IFS%20and%20political%20drama.%20Directed%20by%20Sudhanshu%20Saria%2C%20releasing%20July%205%2C%202024.%20Suhana%20faces%20risks%20and%20betrayal%20in%20a%20dangerous%20personal%20conspiracy%2C%20featuring%20Parveez%20Shaikh%2C%20Atika%20Chauhan%2C%20and%20Gulshan%20Devaiah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fulajh-teaser-out-janhvi-kapoor-takes-on-high-stakes-world-of-ifs%2Farticleshow%2F109367436.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Science%20Behind%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20Ceremony%20At%20Ayodhya's%20Ram%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20noon%2C%20today%2C%20the%20grand%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20witnessed%20a%20unique%20event%20as%20the%20forehead%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20was%20anointed%20with%20a%20ray%20of%20sunlight%2C%20known%20as%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Ram%20Navami.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20cutting-edge%20scientific%20expertise%2C%20a%205.8%20centimetre%20beam%20of%20light%20hit%20the%20deity's%20forehead.%20To%20achieve%20this%20remarkable%20phenomenon%2C%20a%20specialised%20instrument%20was%20designed.%20A%20team%20of%20ten%20esteemed%20Indian%20scientists%20stationed%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20ensured%20the%20success%20of%20this%20auspicious%20event%20on%20Ram%20Navami.%20For%20approximately%203%20to%203.5%20minutes%20starting%20at%2012%20noon%2C%20sunlight%20was%20precisely%20directed%20onto%20the%20statue's%20forehead%20using%20a%20combination%20of%20mirrors%20and%20lenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommissioned%20by%20the%20temple%20trust%2C%20scientists%20from%20a%20leading%20government%20institution%20devised%20a%20sophisticated%20apparatus%20consisting%20of%20mirrors%20and%20lenses.%20This%20mechanism%2C%20officially%20termed%20the%20'Surya%20Tilak%20mechanism'%2C%20marks%20a%20significant%20scientific%20and%20engineering%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Ramacharla%2C%20Scientist%20and%20Director%20at%20the%20Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%20(CBRI)%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20explained%20to%20NDTV%20the%20intricate%20workings%20of%20the%20optomechanical%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opto-mechanical%20system%20consists%20of%20four%20mirrors%20and%20four%20lenses%20fitted%20inside%20the%20tilt%20mechanism%20and%20piping%20systems.%20The%20complete%20cover%20with%20an%20aperture%20for%20the%20tilt%20mechanism%20is%20placed%20at%20the%20top%20floor%20to%20divert%20the%20sun%20rays%20through%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%20to%20the%20Garbha%20Girha%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Ramacharla%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20final%20lens%20and%20mirror%20focus%20the%20sun%20rays%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20Shree%20Ram%20facing%20east.%20The%20tilt%20mechanism%20is%20used%20to%20adjust%20the%20first%20mirror's%20tilt%2C%20sending%20the%20sun%20rays%20towards%20the%20north%20direction%20to%20the%202nd%20mirror%20to%20make%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20on%20every%20year's%20Shree%20Ram%20Navami.%20All%20the%20piping%20and%20other%20parts%20are%20manufactured%20using%20brass%20material.%20The%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%20are%20of%20very%20high%20quality%20and%20durable%20to%20sustain%20a%20long%20period.%20The%20inner%20surfaces%20of%20pipes%2C%20elbows%2C%20and%20enclosures%20are%20black%20powder-coated%20to%20avoid%20scattering%20of%20sunlight.%20Also%2C%20at%20the%20top%20aperture%2C%20an%20infrared%20filter%20glass%20is%20used%20to%20restrict%20the%20Sun's%20heat%20waves%20from%20falling%20on%20the%20idol's%20forehead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Members%20of%20the%20team%20of%20scientists%20inside%20the%20Garbha%20Griha%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Members%20of%20the%20team%20of%20scientists%20inside%20the%20Garbha%20Griha%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F7nt378dg_surya-tilak-_625x300_17_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20team%20of%20scientists%20inside%20the%20'Garbha%20Griha'%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20the%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20mechanism%20involved%20collaboration%20between%20scientists%20from%20CBRI%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIAP)%2C%20Bengaluru.%20Employing%20a%20special%20gearbox%20and%20using%20reflective%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%2C%20the%20team%20orchestrated%20the%20precise%20alignment%20of%20sunlight%20rays%20from%20the%20temple's%20third%20floor%20to%20the%20inner%20sanctum%20(Garbha%20Griha)%20using%20established%20principles%20of%20solar%20tracking.%20Technical%20support%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20and%20the%20manufacturing%20expertise%20of%20Optica%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20company%2C%20further%20helped%20the%20project's%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Pradeep%20Chauhan%2C%20Scientist%20at%20the%20Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20said%20with%20confidence%20that%20the%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20would%20flawlessly%20anoint%20the%20statue%20of%20Ram%20Lalla.%20Given%20the%20fixed%20date%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20based%20on%20the%20lunar%20calendar%2C%20intricate%20arrangements%20involving%2019%20gears%20were%20implemented%20to%20ensure%20the%20timely%20occurrence%20of%20this%20auspicious%20ritual%2C%20all%20without%20relying%20on%20electricity%2C%20batteries%2C%20or%20iron-based%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20premier%20institution%20in%20the%20field%20of%20astronomy%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20has%20devised%20a%20solution%20to%20reconcile%20the%20apparent%20disparity%20between%20the%20lunar%20and%20solar%20(Gregorian)%20calendars.%20%26quot%3BWe%20possess%20the%20requisite%20expertise%20in%20positional%20astronomy%2C%26quot%3B%20elaborated%20Dr%20Annapurni%20Subramaniam%2C%20Director%20of%20IIA%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20expertise%20was%20applied%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Sun's%20rays%2C%20symbolised%20by%20a%20'Surya%20Tilak'%2C%20could%20ceremoniously%20anoint%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lala%20on%20every%20Ram%20Navmi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20from%20CSIR-CBRI%20includes%20Dr%20SK%20Panigrahi%2C%20Dr%20RS%20Bisht%2C%20Mr%20Kanti%20Solanki%2C%20Mr%20V.%20Chakradhar%2C%20Mr%20Dinesh%2C%20and%20Mr%20Sameer.%20Prof.%20R.%20Pradeep%20Kumar%2C%20Director%20of%20CSIR-CBRI%2C%20mentored%20the%20project.%20From%20IIA%20Bangalore%2C%20Dr%20Annapurni%20S.%2C%20Director%20of%20IIA%2C%20Er%20S%20Sriram%2C%20and%20Professor%20Tushar%20Prabhu%20are%20the%20consultants.%20Mr%20Rajinder%20Kotaria%2C%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Optica%2C%20and%20his%20team%2C%20Mr%20Nagraj%2C%20Mr%20Vivek%2C%20and%20Mr%20Thava%20Kumar%2C%20are%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20execution%20and%20installation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20'Surya%20Tilak'%20mechanism%20a