20soil%20to%20cultivate%20spices%20like%20bay%20leaf%20and%20saffron.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKnow%20when%20to%20fertilise%20the%20plant%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20have%20already%20added%20cow%20dung%20compost%20and%20neem%20%3Cem%3Ekhali%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20the%20soil%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20need%20to%20fertilise%20the%20soil%20frequently.%20Right%20before%2015%20days%20of%20flowering%20season%2C%20add%20a%20handful%20of%20vermicompost%20in%20the%20pot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvest%20spices%20at%20the%20right%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Anshu%20says%20different%20spices%20have%20varied%20stages%20of%20flowering%20and%20production.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20spices%20like%20cumin%20and%20coriander%20are%20ready%20for%20harvest%20within%20five%20months%20whereas%20black%20pepper%20takes%20two%20to%20three%20years%20and%20cardamom%20takes%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20she%20is%20stocking%20her%20kitchen%20cabinets%20with%20cumin%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekalonji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%2C%20fenugreek%2C%20and%20fennel.%20Dr%20Anshu%20says%20these%20spices%20have%20a%20distinct%20aroma%20compared%20to%20those%20available%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20use%20of%20chemicals%2C%20harmful%20fertilisers%2C%20colours%2C%20and%20additives%20is%20a%20huge%20concern%20in%20commercially%20packaged%20spices.%20With%20these%20tips%2C%20you%20can%20grow%20your%20own%20spices%20at%20home%20and%20save%20your%20family%20from%20the%20perils%20of%20toxic%20spices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Anshu%20Rathi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712930219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGardening-2-1712929222.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttarakhand-based%20Dr%20Anshu%20Rathi%20stocks%20her%20kitchen%20cabinet%20with%20homegrown%20Indian%20spices%2C%20such%20as%20turmeric%2C%20black%20pepper%2C%20saffron%2C%20cloves%2C%20bay%20leaf%2C%20cardamom%20and%20more.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20grows%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347211%2Fhow-to-grow-spices-at-home-dr-anshu-tripathi-shares-tips-garden-uttarakhand-roorkee%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elections%202024%3A%20How%20Can%20People%20With%20Disabilities%20Vote%20From%20Home%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKavya%20had%20just%20turned%2019%20and%20was%20excited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20because%20she%20was%20older%20but%20because%20she%20would%20exercise%20her%20right%20to%20vote%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20polling%20day%2C%20she%20visited%20the%20booth%20with%20her%20family%20and%20her%20excitement%20waned.%20The%20polling%20station%20was%20not%20accessible%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperson%20with%20a%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20stairs%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20EVMs%2C%20she%20wondered%20how%20she%20would%20cast%20her%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20officials%20on%20duty%20finally%20guided%20her%20to%20the%20back%20entrance%20which%20he%20claimed%20had%20a%20ramp%20attached.%20She%20rolled%20down%20the%20way%20only%20to%20find%20two%20flimsy%20wooden%20planks%20bridging%20an%20almost%20foot-long%20difference.%20With%20four%20people%20supporting%20her%20wheelchair%2C%20and%20a%20heavy%20feeling%20of%20being%20let