vernment-turns-waste-sand-into-eco-friendly-silica-bricks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20dust%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20and%20the%20family%20exhausted%20all%20their%20money%20in%20treatment.%20But%2C%20he%20could%20not%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20she%20refused%20to%20be%20recorded.%20She%20complained%20that%2C%20like%20me%2C%20many%20people%20visit%20them%2C%20click%20photos%2C%20and%20never%20come%20back.%20I%20was%20embarrassed.%20But%20that%20day%2C%20I%20promised%20myself%20that%20I%20would%20strive%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20these%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Samit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20families%20of%20workers%20who%20died%20due%20to%20silicosis%20are%20compensated%20by%20the%20Government.%20In%202003%2C%20he%20established%20OSHAJ%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20such%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20even%20when%20I%20was%20accused%20of%20witchcraft%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20Samit%20travels%20from%20village%20to%20village%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal%20to%20document%20the%20occupational%20and%20clinical%20histories%20of%20the%20workers%20and%20to%20collect%20chest%20X-ray%20plates%20from%20the%20workers%20for%20medical%20tests.%20After%20identifying%20patients%2C%20he%20encourages%20them%20to%20find%20alternate%20employment%20and%20helps%20their%20families%20get%20monetary%20compensation%20from%20the%20Government%20in%20case%20the%20patient%20is%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20process%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20whenever%20I%20would%20voice%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20workers%2C%20I%20would%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20meetings.%20People%20started%20avoiding%20me%20and%20accusing%20me%20of%20practising%20witch-hunting.%20But%20eventually%2C%20they%20shared%20their%20documents%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20started%20fighting%20for%20the%20silicosis-affected%20community%20in%202006%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20workers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345643%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESamit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20workers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20has%20been%20immense%20politics%20right%20from%20the%20hospital%20level%20to%20the%20state%20officials.%20Many%20times%2C%20doctors%20also%20refuse%20to%20write%20correct%20reports%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20higher%20authorities.%20We%20keep%20making%20rounds%20of%20the%20officials%20at%20the%20district%20levels%20to%20get%20these%20families%20their%20compensation%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20knocking%20on%20several%20official%20doors%2C%20Samit%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20on%208%20October%2C%202007%2C%20to%20seek%20their%20support%20for%20the%20relief%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20and%20their%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20amount%20of%20allocation%2C%20it%20directs%20the%20Government%20to%20provide%20Rs%204%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20the%20kin%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Samit%20says%2C%20his%20organisation%20was%20able%20to%20source%20compensation%20amounts%20worth%20Rs%2013.52%20crore%20for%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20Rs%2088%20lakh%20from%20donors%20in%2010%20years%20in%20both%20states%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20silicosis%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20says%20that%20the%20monetary%20support%20from%20the%20Government%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20these%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20breadwinners%20of%20the%20families%20die%2C%20young%20orphan%20children%20are%20forced%20to%20migrate%20for%20earning%20opportunities%20and%20lose%20their%20right%20to%20education.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20monetary%20compensation%20is%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20Many%20families%20have%20used%20these%20amounts%20to%20set%20up%20small%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20children%20but%20whenever%20I%20see%20young%20kids%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%20it%20aches%20my%20heart.%20Thankfully%2C%20with%20our%20small%20efforts%2C%20we%20can%20protect%20the%20future%20generations%20of%20some%20such%20workers.%20Now%20as%20I%20am%20getting%20old%2C%20I%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20my%20experience%20to%20dedicated%20people%20so%20that%20this%20work%20does%20not%20stop%20even%20after%20me.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20organisation%20by%202025.%20We%20also%20require%20decent%20funding%20support%20to%20continue%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Samit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20support%20him%20in%20his%20mission%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20at%20roshniforlabour%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsociety%2Ftheres-a-scourge-of-silicosis-among-mine-and-factory-workers-in-jharkhand%2Farticle65092384.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreathless%3A%20Silicosis%20is%20killing%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3EBy%20Vikram%20Raj%20for%20The%20Hindu%20published%20on%204%20March%202022.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712749731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Jharkhand's%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20has%20helped%20families%20of%20workers%20who%20died%20due%20to%20incurable%20silicosis%20get%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2013%20crores.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345628%2Fjharkhand-samit-kumar-carr-helps-silicosis-patients-get-monetary-compensation-from-government-nhrc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karim%E2%80%99s%20to%20Peter%20Cat%3A%20The%20Fascinating%20Tales%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Legendary%20Restaurants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20to%20savour%20the%20taste%20of%20nostalgia%20coupled%20with%20a%20great%20gastronomic%20experience%2C%20